---
title: Irish Sirloin Steak and Chorizo Salsa with roast potatoes and rocket salad
description: The chorizo salsa that garnishes the sirloin steak in this recipe is tangy and slightly spicy. It's complemented by paprika-roasted potatoes with the faintest hint of piquancy.
